data.description: Golf course home on 10,200 SF lot at Mesa Del Sol with RV access, huge yard and gorgeous views from 2nd floor balcony. Open great room floor plan. Living area with vaulted ceiling, fireplace and sliding doors to full covered patio. Kitchen with cooktop and built in ovens opens to dining area. Downstairs bathroom with tile shower. Upstairs 3 bedrooms, full hall bath & primary bedroom with walk in closet, jetted tub, tile shower, wood floor and sliding doors to patio. Extra room downstairs used as office.
